      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MOET MAGIC (1) has a strong record this track and trip with three wins and two placings from six starts. Was out of the placings last time (30.61) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing fourth and beaten 11 lengths. Rates a leading player. SOIREE (5) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in four starts, including two wins and two placings. Was out of the placings last time (35.11) at Dubbo in a NG, finishing fourth and beaten 9 lengths. Suited here and expected to run well. CANYA HELLFIRE (2) is having his first run over this longer distance. Comes here after a last start 4th and beaten 6 lengths (30.20) at this track. Can hit the frame with the right run. STARFIRE TEARS (7) was a winner two back then strongly fancied last time but could only manage a second (41.51) at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors.",
